    <h3><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">3. Environment Variables<o:p></o:p></span></h3>
    <blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        <pre></pre>
      </blockquote>
      Check the environment variables setting on your computer to make sure also
      required executables are in the PATH and library in the LD_LIBRARY_PATH<br />
